DASHING santas are being offered free bus travel. Santas get bus boost DASHING santas are being offered free bus travel.Runners and walkers taking part in this year's annual Santa Dash in December will be offered free travel on First Glasgow.Friends and family accompanying race participants or passengers dressed as Santa will also get to travel for &pound;1.20, irrespective of the distance travelled.The Santa Dash 5K sets off from George Square at 9.30am on Sunday, December 7 and raises money for the Prince and Princess of Wales Hospice. 